<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>StayNest | AI Powered Homestay Management Platform</title>

    <meta name="description"
        content="StayNest helps independent homestay owners manage listings, reservations, online payments and guests with AI-powered tools.">

    <meta name="keywords"
        content="StayNest, Homestay, Vacation Rental, Property Management, Booking Platform, AI Listing Assistant">

    <link rel="icon" href="/staynesticon.png" type="image/x-icon">

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">

    <style>

        *{
            margin:0;
            padding:0;
            box-sizing:border-box;
        }

        html{
            scroll-behavior:smooth;
        }

        body{
            font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
            background:#faf8f5;
            color:#2d2d2d;
            overflow-x:hidden;
        }

        a{
            text-decoration:none;
        }

        section{
            padding:80px 8%;
        }

        .hero{

            min-height:92vh;

            display:flex;
            align-items:center;
            justify-content:space-between;

            gap:60px;

            background:
            linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.88),rgba(255,255,255,.88)),
            url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505693416388-ac5ce068fe85?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80");

            background-size:cover;
            background-position:center;

        }

        .hero-left{
            flex:1;
        }

        .hero-right{
            flex:1;
            display:flex;
            justify-content:center;
        }

        .hero-right img{

            width:100%;
            max-width:620px;
            border-radius:22px;
            box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.18);

        }

        .tag{

            display:inline-block;

            background:#ffe7d9;

            color:#ff5a3d;

            padding:10px 18px;

            border-radius:50px;

            font-size:14px;

            margin-bottom:22px;

            font-weight:600;

        }

        h1{

            font-size:58px;

            line-height:1.15;

            margin-bottom:25px;

            color:#1f2937;

        }

        h1 span{

            color:#ff5a3d;

        }

        .hero p{

            font-size:19px;

            line-height:1.8;

            color:#555;

            max-width:650px;

            margin-bottom:35px;

        }

        .hero-buttons{

            display:flex;

            gap:18px;

            flex-wrap:wrap;

        }

        .btn{

            padding:15px 28px;

            border-radius:12px;

            font-weight:600;

            transition:.3s;

            display:inline-flex;

            align-items:center;

            justify-content:center;

        }

        .primary{

            background:#ff5a3d;

            color:white;

        }

        .primary:hover{

            background:#eb4728;

            transform:translateY(-3px);

        }

        .secondary{

            border:2px solid #ff5a3d;

            color:#ff5a3d;

            background:white;

        }

        .secondary:hover{

            background:#ff5a3d;

            color:white;

        }

        .stats{

            display:grid;

            grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);

            gap:30px;

            margin-top:60px;

        }

        .stat{

            background:white;

            padding:28px;

            border-radius:18px;

            text-align:center;

            box-shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.08);

        }

        .stat h2{

            color:#ff5a3d;

            font-size:34px;

            margin-bottom:8px;

        }

        .stat p{

            margin:0;

            font-size:15px;

        }

        @media(max-width:1000px){

            .hero{

                flex-direction:column;

                text-align:center;

            }

            h1{

                font-size:42px;

            }

            .hero p{

                margin:auto auto 35px;

            }

            .hero-buttons{

                justify-content:center;

            }

            .stats{

                grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);

            }

        }

        @media(max-width:650px){

            h1{

                font-size:34px;

            }

            .stats{

                grid-template-columns:1fr;

            }

        }

    </style>

</head>

<body>

<%- include("../partials/navbar.ejs") %>

<section class="hero">

<div class="hero-left">

<div class="tag">

🚀 AI Powered Homestay Management Platform

</div>

<h1>

Welcome,

<span>

<%= currUser ? currUser.username : "Guest" %>

</span>

<br>

Manage Homestays Smarter with <span>StayNest</span>

</h1>

<p>

StayNest is a next-generation homestay management platform built for independent property owners. Create professional listings, manage reservations, accept secure online payments, track bookings, and soon leverage AI to generate property descriptions, pricing suggestions, and guest communication—all from one unified dashboard.

</p>

<div class="hero-buttons">

<form action="/listings" method="GET">

<button class="btn primary">

Explore Properties

</button>

</form>

<form action="/listings/new" method="GET">

<button class="btn secondary">

List Your Property

</button>

</form>

</div>

<div class="stats">

<div class="stat">

<h2>24/7</h2>

<p>Booking Availability</p>

</div>

<div class="stat">

<h2>AI</h2>

<p>Listing Assistant</p>

</div>

<div class="stat">

<h2>Secure</h2>

<p>Stripe Payments</p>

</div>

<div class="stat">

<h2>Smart</h2>

<p>Reservation Management</p>

</div>

</div>

</div>

<div class="hero-right">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1566073771259-6a8506099945?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80">

</div>

</section>
<!-- ================= FEATURES ================= -->

